{"tid":249760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛呃like工作室曝光","createTime":"2017-05-19T14:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T16:54:18.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a8ecdef0a3ef6c8ab6b9e48ed7ea4bc573d88f4","tid":249760,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T14:16:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3-like%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0-%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1-%E9%95%B7%E5%9F%8E-%E7%84%A1%E9%96%93%E6%96%B7%E8%AE%9A%E5%A5%BD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3-like%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25BB%25A0-%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%259F%258E-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%2596%25B7%25E8%25AE%259A%25E5%25A5%25BD%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a3e0776a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3-like%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25BB%25A0-%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%259F%258E-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%2596%25B7%25E8%25AE%259A%25E5%25A5%25BD%2F&h=23a2d0d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3-like%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0-%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1-%E9%95%B7%E5%9F%8E-%E7%84%A1%E9%96%93%E6%96%B7%E8%AE%9A%E5%A5%BD/</a><br />\n<br />\n廣州一家市場推廣公司UChina Company擔任董事的Artem Zhdanov，月初在其facebook分享一條短片，聲稱是一間位於深圳的「like工廠」中的情況，片段迅即被廣傳。片段中數百部智能電話組成一幅幅「電話牆」，仿如電話長城，每部電話上的畫面不斷自行變動，為客戶的微信帳戶炮製讚好及評論。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯媒體《RT News》引述Zhdanov指，片段中的智能電話，排列整齊地置放架上，互相有線路連接，並由兩部電腦操縱，主要是登入不同的微信帳戶，為特定微信帳號推高讚好、留言及瀏覽量。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，片段中的「like工廠」已不算大規模，有更大型的like工廠，能同時控制逾萬部電話。<br />\n<br />\n內地以水軍在網上製造虛假好評時有所聞，早前大陸一齣電視劇《孤芳不自賞》，便被爆出「買水軍刷好評，後賴賬不付款」，結果被大量「水軍」在微博、豆瓣論壇追討薪水。不久前一齣電視劇，更造出一天超逾15億的播放量，較全國人口還多的笑話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chinartem/videos/1427378633992570/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchinartem%2Fvideos%2F1427378633992570%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=83ef3388\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chinartem/videos/1427378633992570/</a>"},{"pid":"c96567a1b33b726c56ed8d30d4a32aeec088f416","tid":249760,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T14:55:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ce1320dc726a2dab98d8f951cd51585dadae5c7","tid":249760,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:54:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}